Description: Legendary martial arts director Liu Chia-liang (a.k.a. Lau Kar
Leung) strikes gold as he directs the golden robed real life hero Monk San
Te played by his half-brother Liu Chia-hui (a.k.a. Gordon Liu). Gordon
reprises the role that shot him into superstardom in The 36th Chamber of
Shaolin in the official second sequel Disciples of the 36th Chamber. Per
usual, Liu's action direction is mind-boggling and never ceases to amaze.
